resources.description: Situations concerning that since we are not able to monitor the charging status on traditional batteries charger, which leads overcharge or lack of charge and a single batteries charger is not capable to offer enough power where there needs large charging power. Demonstrating a project adding the CAN Bus system on batteries chargers which will connect with the battery management system and that will achieve the aim of real -time monitoring without any overcharge and lack of charge. This project also results in multi-charger network which makes chargers coordinate to work with avoiding the fact of limited output power. And illustrates details in the processing of the designation of both hardware and software of the CAN Bus system.
resources.name: Research on CAN Bus System for Batteries
